Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.91,0:00:26.55,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你說點什麼啊 哈爾希洛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.90,0:00:27.45,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}唔?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.10,0:00:30.25,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊...我想想...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.85,0:00:33.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家昨晚睡得好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.35,0:00:35.45,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這算啥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.45,0:00:37.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯~ 睡得很熟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.80,0:00:38.40,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.20,0:00:40.70,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}醒過來就天亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.20,0:00:42.30,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然一直就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.30,0:00:44.00,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嘛 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.00,0:00:45.45,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我沒怎麼睡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.16,0:00:46.91,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.68,0:00:50.35,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}其實我是在想馬納多的事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.65,0:00:54.75,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}讓我問一個問題 哈爾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.25,0:00:56.00,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哈爾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.70,0:00:57.45,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你現在冷靜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.85,0:01:04.55,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果我是一個人 面前站著殺了馬納多的哥布林
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.80,0:01:08.00,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那我肯定就握著短刀衝上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.20,0:01:11.25,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣是不是不太像我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.00,0:01:14.70,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.75,0:01:17.95,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是你不是一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.70,0:01:19.30,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.20,0:01:21.25,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不是一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.40,0:01:23.70,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有大家再 我也在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.80,0:01:27.40,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以各位 要活著回來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.40,0:01:29.30,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂喂 請問哈爾市怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.30,0:01:30.35,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}藍德好煩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.55,0:01:34.55,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那天 我們害死了馬納多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.00,0:01:38.65,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想我一生不會忘記這份痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.25,0:01:41.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以這次一定要活著回來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.20,0:01:46.60,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在的我們 有彼此 有梅麗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.70,0:01:51.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也是 害死過同伴的神官
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.05,0:01:54.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們害死了神官
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.05,0:01:57.85,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以絕對不會再讓任何一個人死去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.75,0:01:59.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}梅麗也是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.20,0:02:13.10,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.85,0:02:16.60,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我會保護好你們的性命
